## Description

This is the web frontend code of the `PaperDaily` project based on [`Vue.js`](https://vuejs.org) & [`iView`](http://v3.iviewui.com/).

> node.js 版本建议为v16

## Quick Start

1. Install dependencies

```bash
$ npm install
```

2. Run

```bash
$ npm run dev
```

3. Build

```bash
$ npm run build
```
